{"tid":377534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇戲遇到嘅仆街","createTime":"2017-08-27T18:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T02:51:28.000Z","uid":65872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a310db7f03b609fdca511eed21eb4e007d21a86","tid":377534,"uid":65872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T18:13:28.000Z","msg":"最近去戲院睇戲，一開始個氣氛都好好。<br />\n點知後面有個人不停講野，愈講就愈大聲，我一路睇戲一路聽影評啊？<br />\n我重複，係成套戲，冇停止過發出聲音。係咪on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢係咪當係自己屋企睇戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經有人噓過佢，都仲可以繼續講野。<br />\n然後我都睇到忟再噓佢，佢都係繼續無視世人嘅目光。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隔離有條女用氣聲講野，佢夠膽死話聽唔到大聲啲，屌俾枝咪你好唔好啊。<br />\n要講野要配音返屋企睇啦，我買飛入場唔係想聽影評啊咪撚咁自私啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2eb9bfcf2111f403c749c197cbc17310534b49","tid":377534,"uid":55637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T18:23:00.000Z","msg":"月經post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當面屌柒佢啦，上連登post黎無人幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3dd1253896e476cdd7d22a6febf3b5ad9260dd1","tid":377534,"uid":65872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T02:51:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>月經post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當面屌柒佢啦，上連登post黎無人幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n場戲都睇完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想提醒大家睇戲俾啲公德心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c